                           <li> Most work in this regard was based on research paper published by <a href="http://hplabs.hp.com/techreports/2005/HPL-2005-14.pdf">Lim, Wu, Yen</a> from HP Image Labs. (<a href="https://get.adobe.com/reader/">Download Adobe Acrobat Reader</a>)</li>
